# Project Rule

Before doing anything, read docs/AGENTS.md, docs/DOMAIN_RULES.md and
docs/MVP.md in this repo. Treat them as binding instructions, not background.

This project is currently Phase 0: a local Python library that ports
existing VBA macro logic (see reference/vba_original/, original source,
read-only) for construction price matching into tested code. No web
server, no database, no Docker — see docs/MVP.md for exact scope and
porting order.

Never invent construction pricing rules or prices. docs/DOMAIN_RULES.md
was extracted from real working macros, not designed speculatively — if a
rule there seems unclear or wrong, ask rather than guessing or "improving"
it silently. When porting a function, check reference/vba_original/ for
exact original behavior if DOMAIN_RULES.md is ambiguous.
